Package: moat
Title: Microbiome Omics Audit Toolkit for Pre-Analysis Risk Assessment
Version: 0.99.0
Author: Francesc Català-Moll [aut, cre] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2354-8648>)
Maintainer: Francesc Català-Moll <fcatala@irsicaixa.es>
Authors@R: 
    person("Francesc", "Català-Moll", , "fcatala@irsicaixa.es", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2354-8648"))
Description: Microbiome Omics Audit Toolkit (MOAT) provides a pre-analysis
    audit layer for microbiome and omics studies. It checks design confounding,
    batch-associated microbiome structure, correction identifiability, validation
    leakage, and risk diagnostics, then turns those diagnostics into conservative
    analysis-plan recommendations before downstream statistical or machine
    learning workflows are run.
